data.description: Located on a cul de sac, in historic Glendale, this lovingly updated and open ranch offers 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, with a finished basement. Potential for 4th bedroom in the lower level. A bonus room off of the garage works well as an office, mudroom, or gym. The home is a true gem for those seeking both space and functionality.  Your meticulously landscaped yard is perfect for outdoor activities, from morning coffee on the patio to a fun evening with friends.  Additional 800+ sqft located in finished lower level.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful ranch home yours. Schedule your private tour today!
